{{!--
  Command List Partial
  Displays CLI commands grouped by feature category.

  Expected context:
    - categories  {array}   Category objects from features.json. Each feature within
                            may carry a `cliCommand` string.
    - stats       {object}  Stats object: totalCommands, commandGroups
    - cliName     {string}  The CLI binary name (e.g. "skillmeat", "mytool").
                            Used in the Core Commands code block and help hint.
                            Defaults to the first word of any cliCommand found, or
                            "cli" if none is present.

  Handlebars helpers required by the build script:
    - hasCliCommands(features)  → returns true when at least one feature has cliCommand
    - cliCommands(features)     → returns a comma-separated string of unique cliCommand values

  The "Core Commands" block below is intentionally left as a static template
  with placeholder comments. Replace the bash block with your project's actual
  core commands, or generate it dynamically via a custom helper/partial.
--}}
